{
  "page": "Bell Tower",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Bell Tower</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> or <b>bell tower</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> is one of the towers of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Layout\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Layout</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Layout\">Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bell_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Layout\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>A covered bridge connects the fourth floor of the bell tower with the second floor of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rookery\" title=\"Rookery\">rookery</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bell_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bell_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a> sees the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_comet\" title=\"Red comet\">red comet</a> in the sky above the Bell Tower and the <a href=\"/index.php/Guards_Hall\" title=\"Guards Hall\">Guards Hall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After his <a href=\"/index.php/Capture_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Capture of Winterfell\">capture of Winterfell</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> sees a half-<a href=\"/index.php/Moon\" title=\"Moon\">moon</a> above the Bell Tower.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The bridge between the Bell Tower and the rookery collapses into the yard as a result of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Sack of Winterfell\">sack of Winterfell</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">House Bolton</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bell_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a> includes the bell tower and its covered bridge while making a snow castle of Winterfell at the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bell_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>They assembled by the <a href=\"/index.php/Hunter%27s_Gate\" title=\"Hunter&#39;s Gate\">Hunter's Gate</a> as the first pale rays of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sun\" title=\"Sun\">sun</a> brushed the top of the Bell Tower, their breath frosting in the cold morning air.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bell_Tower&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_50\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 50\">Chapter 50</a>, Theon IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_69\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 69\">Chapter 69</a>, Bran VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_8\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 8\">Chapter 8</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_80\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 80\">Chapter 80</a>, Sansa VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok4.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</